  "text": "The acoustic quantification (AQ) method allows instantaneous cavity measurements to provide on-line assessment of atrial volumes, and the usefulness of AQ to assess atrial volume and function has been validated in a previous study [CITATION_1] . The present study was designed to assess the impact of PAF on LA reservoir, conduit and booster pump function in hypertensive patients, and to identify the clinical factors influencing this relation.",
